    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $input.first().json;\n\nconst platformContext = d.platform === \"tiktok\"\n  ? `TIKTOK SCORING CONTEXT:\n- Views are the PRIMARY signal, not followers or engagement rate\n- A single viral video (10x+ average views) defines account quality\n- Engagement rate is naturally unstable on TikTok — do NOT penalize for this\n- Follower count is almost meaningless\n- Shares are a strong virality signal\n- View spikes = algorithm pickup signal`\n  : `INSTAGRAM SCORING CONTEXT:\n- Engagement rate is the PRIMARY signal (above 3% = strong, below 1% = red flag)\n- Comments carry more weight than likes\n- Niche consistency across posts matters\n- Large following + low engagement = bought/dead audience\n- One viral post means less than CONSISTENT performance`;\n\nconst prompt = `You are an influencer scouting analyst. Analyze this creator and respond with ONLY valid JSON (no markdown, no commentary).\n\nCREATOR DATA:\nUsername: ${d.username}\nPlatform: ${d.platform}\nFollowers: ${d.followers}\nAvg Views (last 10 posts): ${d.avg_views}\nAvg Likes: ${d.avg_likes}\nAvg Comments: ${d.avg_comments}\nEngagement Rate: ${d.engagement_rate}%\nVerified: ${d.is_verified}\nBusiness Account: ${d.is_business}\n\n${platformContext}\n\nRECENT POSTS:\n${JSON.stringify(d.posts_for_gemini)}\n\nRespond with ONLY this JSON:\n{\n  \"category\": \"beauty|tech|finance|fitness|food|fashion|gaming|education|comedy|travel|lifestyle|other\",\n  \"strategic_tier\": \"SAFE BET\" | \"GROWTH BET\" | \"EXPERIMENTAL/VIRAL BET\",\n  \"score\": 0-100,\n  \"outreach_priority\": \"low\" | \"medium\" | \"high\",\n  \"reasoning\": \"3-5 sentences, direct, references actual data\",\n  \"timing_insight\": \"1-2 sentences on best posting days/times\",\n  \"content_trend\": \"1-2 sentences on what content performs best\",\n  \"engagement_verdict\": \"real\" | \"suspicious\" | \"mixed\",\n  \"growth_signal\": \"growing\" | \"stable\" | \"declining\",\n  \"post_breakdown\": [{\"date\":\"YYYY-MM-DD\",\"views\":number,\"likes\":number,\"comments\":number,\"performance\":\"high\"|\"average\"|\"low\"}]\n}`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...d, gemini_prompt: prompt } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
